        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "680b",
          "text": "I first met Helena in the autumn of 2001 at Schumacher College in Devon, England, when she came to speak to the MSc in Holistic Science I was enrolled in. At the time her organization was called the International Society for Ecology and Culture (ISEC) and was headquartered just up the road from the college. Since then Helena and I have stayed in touch, connecting through Findhorn, the Global Ecovillage Network, Gaia Education and her ongoing work through Local Futures and with the International Alliance for Localisation.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 472,
              "href": "https://www.localfutures.org/wp-content/uploads/Local-Futures-Annual-Report-2019.pdf",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 459,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 525,
              "href": "https://www.localfutures.org/programs/global-to-local/international-alliance-localization/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 486,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_4",
          "href": null,
          "name": "48ec",
          "text": "In 2007, we were both attending a meeting of the GEESE (Global Ecovillage Educators for a Sustainable Earth) at Wongsanith Ashram in Thailand. I had brought a video-camera to shoot a series of interviews with the many elders of the ecovillage movement. Helena asked me to volunteer as her camera man for a series of interviews she ended up using in her award winning movie ‘The Economics of Happiness’. At the time I also recorded an interview with her (see here) and I am delighted to have had the chance to follow up 12 years later (recording below).",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 462,
              "href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ae2QmCmJ39w",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 458,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_5",
          "href": null,
          "name": "9614",
          "text": "The Economics of Happiness, Award-winning Doctumentary by Helena Norberg-Nodge",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": {
            "mediaResource": {
              "href": "https://vimeo.com/162302072"
            }
          },
          "layout": "INSET_CENTER",
          "markups": [],
          "type": "IFRAME"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_6",
          "href": null,
          "name": "3d12",
          "text": "Earlier this year I reconnected with Helena and her husband John Page again during an event in Madrid called ‘Despierta! El planeta te necesita 2019’ (Wake up! The planet needs you 2019). This autumn her new book ‘Local is our Future: Steps to an economics of happiness’ was published and Helena kindly sent me a copy. Highly recommended! This prompted me to suggest making time for the conversation you can watch below.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 148,
              "href": "https://www.lacasaencendida.es/encuentros/despierta-planeta-te-necesita-2019-9966",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 110,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_7",
          "href": null,
          "name": "1a20",
          "text": "Here is a brief summary of what we talk about:",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_8",
          "href": null,
          "name": "a7c6",
          "text": "the need for economic systems change in order to effectively respond to climate change",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_9",
          "href": null,
          "name": "2d1f",
          "text": "our structurally dysfunctional economic and monetary system as a more upstream intervention point than the symptoms of inequality, climate change, poverty, ecosystems collapse and other aspects of the converging crises humanity now faces",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_10",
          "href": null,
          "name": "d1a3",
          "text": "the growing call for re-localisation and re-regionalisation in the context of the diverse and growing new economy movement and the re-design of capitalism",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_11",
          "href": null,
          "name": "c9d2",
          "text": "shifts in the language of politics and public discourse triggered by Extinction Rebellion and Fridays for Future, and the simultaneous persistence of lack of action driven by mistaken convictions (eg like that technology creates jobs, that economic growth is a necessity for quality of life …)",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_12",
          "href": null,
          "name": "e85a",
          "text": "the insufficiency of GDP as a measure of success and the role of both quantitative and qualitative indicators in defining more meaningful measures of success",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_13",
          "href": null,
          "name": "5eed",
          "text": "the rigged playing field of neo-liberal economics that destroyed local communities, deregulated global finance while regulating against local place-based businesses and favouring multinational corporations with their huge degenerative impacts",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_14",
          "href": null,
          "name": "3435",
          "text": "the rise of extremism and the influence of media",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_15",
          "href": null,
          "name": "0e39",
          "text": "the urgent need to regulate banks and global finance while decreasing the restrictive regulations at local and regional scale through increased accountability and transparency within the regional economy",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_16",
          "href": null,
          "name": "ca18",
          "text": "the degenerative impact of hidden subsidies and externalities",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "a185",
          "text": "the ongoing practice of ‘insane trade’ where countries import and export roughly equal amounts of the same product rather than enabling local production for local consumption",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 37,
              "href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l8XJ_fg1xMc",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 25,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_18",
          "href": null,
          "name": "1e50",
          "text": "Extinction Rebellion, Fridays For Future … the discourse focussed on climate emergency and the lack of discourse and action focussed on local and bioregional transformation and building of alternatives and community resilience to the changes ahead",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_19",
          "href": null,
          "name": "0c37",
          "text": "the importance of working on the local and the global at the same time and the need to connect local communities into an international alliance for relocalisation",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_20",
          "href": null,
          "name": "5b57",
          "text": "the importance of diverse regenerative cultures — emphasis on the plural — as a form of de-colonialization that values diversity and recognises that regenerative cultures are place-sources and hence different in each ecological and cultural context",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_21",
          "href": null,
          "name": "9dc5",
          "text": "the need for deep dialogue between the most urbanised cultures and the place-based rural cultures still existing around the world as a pathway to revaluing rural life and reconnection to place",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_22",
          "href": null,
          "name": "5fda",
          "text": "moving beyond the rich-country and poor-country discourse",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_23",
          "href": null,
          "name": "f75c",
          "text": "activating communities in all their natural diversity through food, the connection between food, human health and ecosystems health, and through a shared connection to the story of place",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_24",
          "href": null,
          "name": "1762",
          "text": "“big picture activism”",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 21,
              "href": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RZd3es18JW8",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 1,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_25",
          "href": null,
          "name": "0549",
          "text": "finding meaning, connection and community in coming home to place",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_26",
          "href": null,
          "name": "127a",
          "text": "the economics of happiness — focussing on living in the present moment and finding deeper meaning in the relationship to place and to community",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_27",
          "href": null,
          "name": "97cb",
          "text": "…",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_28",
          "href": null,
          "name": "6843",
          "text": "I hope you enjoy listening to this conversation between Helena and me as much as I enjoyed talking with her again.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "a91c6f26fe75_29",
          "href": null,
          "name": "84ac",
          "text": "reGeneration Rising!",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
